<h1>Currency Textbox</h1>

<p><code>f-currency-textbox</code> will create a <a href="/api/havok/form/CurrencyTextBox.html">havok/form/CurrencyTextBox</code> which extends <a href="/api/havok/form/NumberTextBox.html">havok/form/NumberTextbox</a> and <a href="/api/havok/form/_ValidationMixin">havok/form/_ValidationMixin</a> to add localized currency formatting.</p>

<h2>Example</h2>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <d-formspy class="form-horizontal">
        <f-currency-textbox label="Cost"></f-currency-textbox>
    </d-formspy>
</div>

<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set currencyTextboxExample1 %}
<f-currency-textbox label="Cost"></f-currency-textbox>{% endset %}{{currencyTextboxExample1|e}}
</pre>

<h3>Currency Box with preset float value</h3>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <d-formspy class="form-horizontal">
        <f-currency-textbox label="Cost" value=2.2></f-currency-textbox>
    </d-formspy>
</div>

<h3>Currency Box with preset string value</h3>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <d-formspy class="form-horizontal">
        <f-currency-textbox label="Cost" value="2.2"></f-currency-textbox>
    </d-formspy>
</div>

<h3>Currency Box with negative value</h3>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <d-formspy class="form-horizontal">
        <f-currency-textbox label="Cost" value="-100"></f-currency-textbox>
    </d-formspy>
</div>
